    "created_at": "2014-10-26T12:22:55Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-01-17T06:29:18Z",
    "body": "There is no native `prompt` dialogs in most GUI toolkits, so implementing `prompt` in atom-shell would require writing the `prompt` dialog from ground up on all platforms. Due to the rare use of `prompt`, I think it doesn't deserve to do all the work, and it is very easy to use a web implemented solution for this.\n\nSo I'm closing this as won't fix.\n"
  },
