    "updated_at": "2016-04-08T07:47:53Z",
    "body": "I made one that works just like the browser `window.prompt` using preload & a synchronous IPC call. Check it out [here](https://github.com/konsumer/electron-prompt). It could use some styling, but you get the idea. ([here](https://github.com/electron/electron-quick-start/compare/master...konsumer:master) are my changes.)\n\n```\nvar name = prompt('What is your name?', 'David')\n```\n\n![prompt](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/83857/14376697/f0b16bca-fd1f-11e5-880b-a8e20d9c84d2.gif)\n"
  },
